  "reviews": "\u201cIt seems to capture the spirit that VIZ is so synonymous with, while combining distinct genres in unique ways.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.gameinformer.com/games/the_world_next_door/b/pc/archive/2018/03/27/combining-narrative-driven-story-with-action-puzzle-combat.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Game Informer</a><br><br>\u201c\u2026it will fill the match-3 shaped hole in my heart...\u201d<br><a href=\"https://compete.kotaku.com/the-world-next-door-turns-magical-brawls-into-puzzles-1826509490\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Kotaku</a><br><br>\u201c...fantasy anime meets Tetris...something endearingly unexpected\u2026\u201d\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.polygon.com/2018/3/27/17168626/the-world-next-door-preview-viz-media-video-game\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Polygon</a><br>",
